    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-07-06T16:29:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-07-06T16:29:00-05:00" n="816"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d816">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 637.119/467</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Assistant to the War Trade Board Representative in
                        Cuba</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Farnsworth</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-07-06T16:00:00-05:29">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 6, 1918, 4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received July 7, 7.07 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your 110, July 2. I have the personal assurance of Cuban authorities that the
                    manner of dealing with Spanish vessels relative to bunkers will be carried out
                    strictly in accordance with your recommendation. Mr. <persName
                        corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_MHH1">Morgan</persName> handed you translation
                    of the President’s decree of June 26 relative to bunkering vessels.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Farnsworth</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
